		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00257" index="257">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jogging is about rhythm.\nBattling is about rhythm, too!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00258" index="258">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">På en måde formoder jeg, at det var en\nslags målstregen.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00259" index="259">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When your rhythm gets thrown off,\neverything seems out of whack.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00260" index="260">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Da jeg joggede den anden dag,\nen vild Pokémon kom efter mig.\rJeg løb så hurtigt, jeg var på toppen af\nbølger, jeg sværger!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00261" index="261">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jogging is about rhythm.\nBattling is about rhythm, too.\fOur rematch is also about rhythm!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00262" index="262">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Emma: We battle together!\nThat’s why we’re tough!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00263" index="263">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Emma: Waaah!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00264" index="264">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Emma: You’re awesome!\nAre you maybe a Pokémon genius?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00265" index="265">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Emma: We won’t play with you if you\ndon’t have two Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00266" index="266">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Emma: When I battle with Lil,\nwe shouldn’t lose!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00267" index="267">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lil: We’re gonna crunch and\nmunch you all up!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00268" index="268">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lil: Hwaaah!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00269" index="269">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lil: We’re going to be tough\nTrainers, too! We decided!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00270" index="270">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lil: Only one Pokémon is too lonesome!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00271" index="271">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lil: Du gumlede os alle sammen sidst\ntid, men det er vores tur nu!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00272" index="272">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hey, check this out! Look at the\nluster of my Pokémon’s fur!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00273" index="273">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hey, hey, did you take a good look?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00274" index="274">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Every day, I brush my Pokémon a\nhundred strokes. Then, I do me.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00275" index="275">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I brushed my party a lot.\nSo we’d be ready for a rematch!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00276" index="276">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m a rookie breeder, but I’ll do\nmy very best!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00277" index="277">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er i orden!\nJeg er stadig en rookie!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00278" index="278">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvordan rejser man Pokémon?\nUmm... Det handler om kærlighed, ikke?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00279" index="279">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can’t be a rookie forever.\nI’ve learned a lot since we last met.\r</language>
	</row>
