	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00302" index="302">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Teri: Yay! We’re gonna battle with\nlots of Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00303" index="303">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Teri: Even with both of us, we lost.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00304" index="304">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Teri: Our mommy is a twin, too.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00305" index="305">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Teri: We want to battle with lots\nof Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00306" index="306">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Teri: Yay! We’re gonna battle with\nlots of Pokémon again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00307" index="307">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tia: Yay! We’re gonna have a battle\nwith three Trainers!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00308" index="308">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tia: We two couldn’t win.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00309" index="309">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tia: Når mor og moster og mig\nog Teri mødes, det er det virkelig\fforvirrende og sjovt!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00310" index="310">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tia: We want to have a battle with\nthree Trainers.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00311" index="311">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tia: Yay! We’re gonna have another\nbattle with three Trainers!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00312" index="312">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min Pokémon hærdede sig fra\narbejder på ranchen.\rJeg er ret stolt af dem!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00313" index="313">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hahahah! Det kan din Pokémon helt sikkert være\nregnet med!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00314" index="314">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Når jeg nusser med min Pokémon, kan jeg\nføler ikke kun deres krops varme, men\fderes medfølelse.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00315" index="315">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hejsa! Du er så hård lille\nTræner! Jeg husker dig!\rTjek min farm-hærdede Pokémon!\nDe er min stolthed og glæde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00316" index="316">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m warmed up and limber.\nI’m OK to battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00317" index="317">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Um...\nI wasn’t emotionally ready.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00318" index="318">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Actually, I wanted to make a run\nfor it... That’s a joke.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00319" index="319">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m going to keep running.\nJust as long as there’s a road...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00320" index="320">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve been training so I can have\na rematch with you.\rI’m OK to battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00321" index="321">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Matt: Uhohoho! I’ll show y’all how\ntightly I’ve bonded with my daughter!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00322" index="322">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Matt: Forældre-og-barn magt kunne ikke\nfå arbejdet gjort.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00323" index="323">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Matt: Jeg regner med båndene mellem jer\nog dine Pokémon er som båndene\fforældre deler med deres børn.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00324" index="324">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Matt: Oh, there’s no way you could\nbeat us both with one Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00325" index="325">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Matt: Ayuh? You’re here to check the\nbond I have with my daughter again?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00326" index="326">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ava: I can get away with slacking\noff if I have my Pokémon out!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00327" index="327">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ava: Oh, sheesh!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00328" index="328">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ava: Papa, I’m sorry! I promise I’ll\nwork harder starting tomorrow!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00329" index="329">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ava: You’re battling me and my pa.\nOne Pokémon won’t cut it, dear!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00330" index="330">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ava: Åh, hej! Det er godt i alle kom\nkalder på os igen!\rJeg kan tage en pause fra arbejdet, hvis jeg er\nkæmper mod Pokémon. Heldigt for mig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00331" index="331">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er en af ​​Ninja Trio!\nAt blive opdaget betyder, at jeg skal kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00332" index="332">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I concede defeat...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00333" index="333">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mit cover er sprængt, så hvad skulle\ngør jeg?\rMåske vil jeg tage nogle konkurrencer ind\nHearthome City. Måske gør jeg det.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00334" index="334">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan du huske mig?\nJeg er en af ​​Ninja Trio!\fAt blive opdaget betyder, at jeg skal kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00335" index="335">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er en af ​​Ninja Trio!\nAt blive opdaget betyder, at jeg skal kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00336" index="336">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I concede defeat...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00337" index="337">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mens jeg gemte mig i det høje græs,\nfornemmede Pokémon overalt omkring mig!\rSkjulende lyde af bevægelse...\nKvælede gråd... Jeg hørte dem!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00338" index="338">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan du ikke huske mig?\nJeg er en af ​​Ninja Trio!\fAt blive opdaget betyder, at jeg skal kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00339" index="339">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er en af ​​Ninja Trio!\nAt blive opdaget betyder, at jeg skal kæmpe!\rMen hvordan opdagede du mig?\nFortæl mig ikke, at du også er en ninja!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00340" index="340">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I concede defeat...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00341" index="341">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A Pokémon Trainer’s good at finding\nstuff, I guess.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00342" index="342">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du skal slutte dig til os, så vi kan danne\nNinja-kvartetten!\rUanset hvad, lad os kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00343" index="343">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du ser ud til at have meget selvtillid.\nLad os se om det er berettiget!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00344" index="344">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Haha!\nA total loss for me!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00345" index="345">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du ser ud til at have en overflod af\ntalent. Det er ret fantastisk.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00346" index="346">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Da jeg tabte til dig sidste gang, var jeg det\nbare uheldig.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00347" index="347">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">As an Ace Trainer, I have to take\nbattles in stride.\rI need to stay cool and calm whether\nI win or lose.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00348" index="348">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Aiyeeeeh!\nWe lost!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00349" index="349">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How dare you beat us!\nGo away! Go!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00350" index="350">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Last time, I got a little emotional\nover losing...\rI’ll stay cool and calm today!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00351" index="351">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Me lose to someone so young?\nI daresay not!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00352" index="352">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The power of youth...\nIt’s startling.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00353" index="353">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Somehow, it makes me happy seeing\na young, yet sure-footed, Trainer\fsuch as yourself.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00354" index="354">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ungdommens kraft og teknikken\naf veteranen...\rLad os kæmpe igen for at se hvilken\nskal sejre!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00355" index="355">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This buff physique isn’t just for\nshow!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00356" index="356">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ugwaaaah!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00357" index="357">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Why? Is it because my training isn’t\nenough?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00358" index="358">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My buff physique!\nFeast your eyes on it again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00359" index="359">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg forskrækkede dig bare!\rMens du stadig kæmper for det\nkom dig, jeg er allerede vinderen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00360" index="360">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, what’s that?\nYou’re supposed to be fumbling more.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00361" index="361">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I need a better reaction out of you.\nI feel silly hiding for so long!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00362" index="362">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har lige set mig, og jeg vil vædde med dig\ntænkte: "Længe ikke set."\rMens du stadig tænker på det, gør jeg det\nallerede være vinderen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00363" index="363">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We ninjas appear where you least\nexpect us!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00364" index="364">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I didn’t expect to lose...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00365" index="365">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When I hide out like this, I think\nabout what it must be like for\fPokémon inside their Poké Balls.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00366" index="366">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wah! Another chance encounter with\na foe who defeated me before!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00367" index="367">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A ninja can use all sorts of cool\ntechniques!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00368" index="368">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hmm...\nMy ninja techniques failed to work...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00369" index="369">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There’s a ninja Gym Leader somewhere\nfar away.\rI should become a devotee of theirs.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00370" index="370">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad er der med dig?\nEr du ikke en ninja endnu?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00371" index="371">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Don’t be shocked when you see my\nPokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00372" index="372">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh... My... Gosh...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00373" index="373">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A dragon Pokémon’s real power is\nnothing like mine!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00374" index="374">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You again?\rYou must really like that dragon\nPokémon I use.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00375" index="375">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil lære dig om charmen ved\nfugl Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00376" index="376">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow. I’ll admit to being surprised\nby that outcome.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00377" index="377">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Synet af dig kæmper...\nDet var simpelthen et vidunder at se!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00378" index="378">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lægger du endelig mærke til det store\nkvaliteter af fugle-Pokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00379" index="379">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Zac: Jen, watch this! I’m going to\nuse everything you’ve taught me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00380" index="380">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Zac: Wow. Someone that’s even\nbetter than Jen...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00381" index="381">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Zac: Jeg er ligeglad med, om jeg kommer til at mødes\nden bedste træner i regionen...\fJeg vil stadig hellere lære af Jen.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00382" index="382">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Zac: Vil du ikke hellere kæmpe\nmed os to?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00383" index="383">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Zac: Denne gang vil jeg ikke svigte dig\n, Jen! Jeg lover!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00384" index="384">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jen: Her kommer en træner.\nZac, er du klar? Lad os gøre dette!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00385" index="385">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jen: I just got embarrassed in front\nof my little buddy here...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00386" index="386">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jen: Zac, I’m so sorry.\nI’m a failure as your instructor.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00387" index="387">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jen: Would you like to have a\ntwo-on-two Pokémon battle with us?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00388" index="388">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jen: Here comes our Trainer!\nAre you ready this time?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00389" index="389">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Look at these beautiful wings!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00390" index="390">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, you!\nI’m going to peck you for that!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00391" index="391">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">People say there’s a bird Pokémon\nthat can learn human speech.\rDo you know anything about it?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00392" index="392">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My bird Pokémon has such gorgeous\nwings.\rIt must have been some sort of a\nmistake that we lost last time!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00393" index="393">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00394" index="394">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00395" index="395">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00396" index="396">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">ZUBAT! Doesn’t that sound like a\nninja bursting from cover?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00397" index="397">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh!\nMy ZUBAT tristars...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00398" index="398">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Så forvirring blandt fjenden er\nen måde en ninja kæmper.\rEn Pokémon kan ikke overvinde sin\nforvirring, medmindre den skifter ud.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00399" index="399">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The shinobi live by speed!\nI’ll get in my attacks before you do!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00400" index="400">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">See how Mt. Coronet towers above us.\nI want to be big like that one day!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00401" index="401">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En kraftfuld tilstedeværelse tårner sig op før\nmig... Det er dig!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00402" index="402">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mt. Coronet has long been known as\nan ancient and mysterious mountain.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00403" index="403">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hmm?! You tower before\nme again?\rIt’s as if you’re Mt. Coronet!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00404" index="404">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hah! Hah!\nI’m psyched for this! Here goes!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00405" index="405">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t get why we can’t win.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00406" index="406">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I guess I ought to study winning\ntechniques for a change...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00407" index="407">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hah! Hah!\nThis time, I’m psyched up!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00408" index="408">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hastighed er en ninjas bedste våben!\nKan du følge med?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00409" index="409">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I did a lot to conceal myself, too...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00410" index="410">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll wait here for a weaker-looking\nTrainer and then ambush them!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00411" index="411">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I became even faster!\nHow can you hope to keep up?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00412" index="412">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I go everywhere with my NOCTOWL.\nWe’re gonna show you owl best! Ha!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00413" index="413">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We did our best. That’s what\nmatters. Right?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00414" index="414">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Even on cold days, just being with\nmy NOCTOWL keeps me warm!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00415" index="415">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I curled up inside my NOCTOWL’s wings\nand waited for you to return!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00416" index="416">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mens jeg udforskede ruinerne, opdagede jeg\nen træner! Jeg må undersøge det!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00417" index="417">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My investigation has revealed the\nTrainer to be tough! Ouch...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00418" index="418">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Celestic Town is an old town.\nI’m sure to find something cool.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00419" index="419">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mens jeg udforskede ruinerne, opdagede jeg\ndig igen! Jeg vil nu undersøge!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00420" index="420">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll have you know my Pokémon\nsleeps on a fancy imported bed.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00421" index="421">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">H-humph! There’s an unseemly sense\nof desperation about you. Ugh!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00422" index="422">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, min stakkels lille kæmper er\nalt sammen ude...\rJeg lader den sove i den seng\nJeg havde sendt fra udlandet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00423" index="423">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I do this only because I love my\nPokémon. Winning isn’t that important.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00424" index="424">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil gerne begynde nu.\nEr du helt forberedt?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00425" index="425">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, how very impressive of you.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00426" index="426">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vil du informere mig om hvem\nden fantastiske underviser du har hyret til\fer din Pokémon?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00427" index="427">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, jeg er glad for at se dig igen.\nEr du forberedt?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00428" index="428">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If it pleases you, would you care for\na Pokémon battle with me?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00429" index="429">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your handling of Pokémon is\nquite impeccable, I must say.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00430" index="430">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Bahaha! Jeg blev inviteret af mesteren\naf Pokémon Mansion.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00431" index="431">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If it pleases you, would you care for\na rematch with me?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00432" index="432">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve never battled a young Trainer\nlike you before. I’m quite nervous!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00433" index="433">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, dear... That wasn’t anything like\nbattling with my friends.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00434" index="434">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Usually, I’ll have matches with\nmembers of my social club.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00435" index="435">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, er det dig igen, skat?\rDet gør mig lidt nervøs at spørge,\nmen må jeg få en omkamp?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00436" index="436">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00437" index="437">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00438" index="438">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00439" index="439">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hold it right there, citizen!\nWalking around at night is unsafe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00440" index="440">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve got tough partners with you.\nCarry on, citizen. Carry on.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00441" index="441">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Out so late? Does your mother\nknow you’re out so late?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00442" index="442">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, hello there!\rThat’s very civil minded of you to\nsay hello to your local Policeman!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00443" index="443">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Didn’t I already give you a warning?\nIt’s unsafe to walk around at night!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00444" index="444">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Are there any shady-looking\ncharacters around here?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00445" index="445">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hold nu bare op. Det sagde jeg ikke\ndu så lyssky ud!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00446" index="446">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Don’t go hanging out with any\nshady-looking characters! You hear?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00447" index="447">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Patrolling night and day sure is\nexhausting... Yawn...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00448" index="448">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er der nogen figurer, der ser lyssky ud?\nJeg er altid på udkig efter punkere.\rForventer nogle lyssky fyr til faktisk\npop up... Gør det mig mærkelig?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00449" index="449">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lad os nyde en hård kamp i\nkølige nattevinde! Brrrr! Forfriskende!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00450" index="450">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det var for mørkt til, at jeg kunne se meget\ntja... Ja... For mørkt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00451" index="451">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ups, jeg må hellere vende tilbage til min\nslå før chefen sender mig i radio...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00452" index="452">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yo! Hanging tough, Trainer? Word!\nI’m trying to make my lingo more hip!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00453" index="453">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Træner du stadig så sent?\rDet gør dig enten til et dårligt barn eller\nen god træner. Hvilken er det?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00454" index="454">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m on patrol seeing whether or not\nthere’s any trouble afoot!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00455" index="455">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Big trouble! Officer in need\nof assistance!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00456" index="456">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your toughness is too much!\nI’m in serious trouble!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00457" index="457">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t know how to say this, but\nmaybe we patrol too much.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00458" index="458">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Let me ask you a question!\nAre you tough enough to take me?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00459" index="459">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan du ikke se, at jeg fisker?\nTal ikke! Du vil skræmme fisken!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00460" index="460">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sheesh... I let a Pokémon, and that\nbattle, get away from me.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00461" index="461">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fiskeri og kamp er delikat\nting - som jeg er. Er det forkert?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00462" index="462">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kan se, jeg fisker, kan du ikke?\nSå tal ikke til mig! Jøss!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00463" index="463">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg ville ønske, at der kom en fiskeglad dame\nlangs. Men nej, det hele er bare trænere.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00464" index="464">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sure, so I lost.\nBut I’ll keep on fishing.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00465" index="465">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis du kender nogle damer der kan lide\nfiskeri, hjælp mig med at synke krogen i dem!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00466" index="466">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Umm... Yeah. Weren’t you that person\nwho preferred Pokémon over fishing?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00467" index="467">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Water Pokémon sure get happy when\nit rains. So do I!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00468" index="468">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oof. Just got trampled right under\nyour feet that time!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00469" index="469">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yup, a kid like you should be running\naround outside, rain or shine.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00470" index="470">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve been fishing here ever since\nI lost to you.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00471" index="471">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Can you keep up with us?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00472" index="472">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve got energy to burn!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00473" index="473">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Uanset hvor hårdt du kæmper, så sørg for\ndu skader aldrig miljøet.\rPrøv ikke at bryde nogen grene eller\ntrampe nogen planter, okay?</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00474" index="474">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej! Du er den højenergiske træner!\nJeg vil vædde på, at du ikke kan følge med os nu!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00475" index="475">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gør du din del for at beskytte\nmiljøet? jeg er!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00476" index="476">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Good. You seem to be a kindhearted\nTrainer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00477" index="477">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">People, Pokémon... All of us!\nWe’re all a part of nature.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00478" index="478">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Heya, long time!\rAre you enjoying your nature-filled\nadventure with Pokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00479" index="479">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vores opgave er at beskytte det naturlige\nmiljøet i denne region.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00480" index="480">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’ve got to get tougher than this...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00481" index="481">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg elsker hvor naturligt det er her.\nJeg ville ønske, jeg kunne bo herude.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00482" index="482">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad synes du? Miljøet\ner uskadt i dette område.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00483" index="483">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00484" index="484">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00485" index="485">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00486" index="486">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00487" index="487">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00488" index="488">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00489" index="489">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00490" index="490">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00491" index="491">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I find it reassuring to be on this\ndamp soil...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00492" index="492">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ufufufufu...\nYou had to beat me...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00493" index="493">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">It feels good to mope here after a\nloss... Ufufufufu...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00494" index="494">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er Damp min favorit Pokémon-evne?\nFufufu... Alt vil gøre...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00495" index="495">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00496" index="496">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00497" index="497">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00498" index="498">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00499" index="499">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00500" index="500">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00501" index="501">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00502" index="502">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00503" index="503">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00504" index="504">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00505" index="505">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m proud of my Pokémon!\nHere, I’ll show you why!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00506" index="506">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Youch! You sure showed me how tough\nyou were.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00507" index="507">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, hvad har vi her?\nDet er en Pokédex!\rDet registrerer Pokémon-data på\nsyn? Jeg har aldrig set en før!\rJeg har hørt du kan flytte solen eller\nmåneikon for at tjekke Pokémon\fhabitatkort efter tidspunkt på dagen!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00508" index="508">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I take down details in my notebook\nabout Pokémon I’ve battled.\rI’ll write more data down about your\nPokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00509" index="509">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh? Here comes a nice-looking\nTrainer. This is worth evaluation.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00510" index="510">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Our research has arrived at this one\nconclusion: you’re a tough one!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00511" index="511">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et stort udvalg af Pokémon lever i\nStore Marsk.\rSer du, for utallige år siden,\nhele dette område lå under havet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00512" index="512">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, hvordan gør du? Må jeg undersøge det\nhvor meget hårdere du er blevet siden\fvores sidste møde?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00513" index="513">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er Pokémon, der bliver flere\nkraftig når det regner.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00514" index="514">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Som regn flyder mine tårer af at miste...\nDe kalder mig Regnkvinden...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00515" index="515">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil gerne vise min smukke frem\nparasol, men den bliver snavset\fi regnen.\rÅh, så stort et dilemma!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00516" index="516">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">On rainy days, I get more energetic!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00517" index="517">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When it rains, I get more tense!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00518" index="518">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er ikke særlig let at prøve at kæmpe\nmens du holder en paraply.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00519" index="519">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis det regnede hver dag, kunne jeg have gjort det\nmin paraply åben hele tiden.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00520" index="520">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er ikke fordi det regner.\nJeg elsker bare paraplyer!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00521" index="521">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve spotted a sneaky Trainer!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00522" index="522">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Defeated by sneakiness...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00523" index="523">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m sorry, it wasn’t “sneaky”!\nIt should have been “tough”!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00524" index="524">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er konstant på patrulje.\nPå den måde er det sikkert selv om natten.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00525" index="525">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Whoa! Hold it right there!\nI’ve spotted a sneaky Trainer!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00526" index="526">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg svømmer hele året rundt.\nJeg taber ikke en kamp på havet!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00527" index="527">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tabte mig i havet...\nMen jeg svømmer hele året rundt!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00528" index="528">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When you’re out at sea, Water-type\nPokémon look more lively.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00529" index="529">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg elsker havet. Det var kun tilfældigt\nsom jeg tabte sidste gang.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00530" index="530">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brr... I’m starting to get chilly.\nI could use a win to get warmed up.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00531" index="531">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Havets kulde, og\nnederlagets kulde...\rDet er et dobbelt puf.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00532" index="532">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Se på mine læber...\nDe er farven på svesker!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00533" index="533">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brr... I’m starting to feel chilly.\nHow about a hot Pokémon battle?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00534" index="534">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej, bølgeridende træner!\nHvad med en kamp på havet?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00535" index="535">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You sure schooled me there.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00536" index="536">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Maybe I should switch to surfing,\ntoo...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00537" index="537">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, hi again!\nYou’re that wave-riding Trainer!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00538" index="538">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hello, there!\nAren’t you going to swim?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00539" index="539">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad er mere salt?\nMine tårer eller havet...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00540" index="540">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er der ikke mange søveje\ndu kan svømme i Sinnoh.\rDet giver mig lyst til at holde ferie\ni Hoenn-regionen.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00541" index="541">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When I see people surfing, I don’t\nfeel jealous or anything.\rI just simply love to swim!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00542" index="542">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Isn’t this nice?\nI love my inner tube!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00543" index="543">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kunne ikke bevæge mig særlig godt pga\nmit indre rør kom i vejen!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00544" index="544">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My mom blew up my inner tube for me.\nI ran out of breath just opening it!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00545" index="545">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kan komme tilbage alt, hvad du vil, men\ndu kan ikke få mit indre rør!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00546" index="546">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ehehe...\nI can battle, too!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00547" index="547">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I lost, and now I feel hungry.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00548" index="548">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">That cloud looks like ice cream!\nI wish I could eat some! Mmm...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00549" index="549">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve been dawdling here all this\ntime!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00550" index="550">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00551" index="551">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00552" index="552">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00553" index="553">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Rejser du alene, er du? Det er\nimponerende! Hvad med at vi kæmper?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00554" index="554">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re good, pip-squeak!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00555" index="555">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Maybe I’ll go work out down at the\nrestaurant again.\rThat place gets different people in\nevery day, and they all like battles.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00556" index="556">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej, ensomme rejsende! Lad os bryde\nmonotonien med endnu en kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00557" index="557">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Awwww!\nI almost had that fish reeled in!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00558" index="558">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You need to have more respect for\na grown-up...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00559" index="559">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You need to settle down some.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00560" index="560">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Aww!\nJeg var lige ved at vælte den fisk ind!\r...Åh nej. Ikke dig igen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00561" index="561">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00562" index="562">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00563" index="563">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00564" index="564">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00565" index="565">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00566" index="566">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00567" index="567">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00568" index="568">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00569" index="569">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Let me demonstrate my technique.\nIt’s how this grown-up battles.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00570" index="570">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">That’s how you attack? Pshaw!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00571" index="571">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re so much more of a Trainer\nthan you look!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00572" index="572">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Give this grown-up another chance to\ndemonstrate her technique.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00573" index="573">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det ser ud til at være meget mystificerende.\nDet er den fornemmelse, jeg får.\rFor at vise dig, hvad jeg mener, vil jeg kæmpe\nmed den Pokémon, jeg fandt.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00574" index="574">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kan ikke vinde med Pokémon, som jeg er\nikke bekendt med...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00575" index="575">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det ser ud til at være meget mystificerende.\nDet er den fornemmelse, jeg får.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00576" index="576">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ah-ha! I found me a Trainer!\rI challenge you to battle with\nthe Pokémon I’ve found!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00577" index="577">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har rejst rundt i verden\njagter historier på mysterier.\rDet har gjort mig ret hård!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00578" index="578">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sigh...\nThat’s a downer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00579" index="579">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er mysterier, der venter på mig\nat undersøge verden rundt.\rDet er ikke tid til at være ked af det\nfor mig selv.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00580" index="580">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er et uendeligt udbud af\nmysterier rundt om i verden.\rAt støde på dig her sker bare\nat være sådan et mysterium!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00581" index="581">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00582" index="582">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00583" index="583">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00584" index="584">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00585" index="585">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00586" index="586">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00587" index="587">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00588" index="588">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00589" index="589">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00590" index="590">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00591" index="591">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00592" index="592">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00593" index="593">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg havde fornemmet tilstedeværelsen af ​​en\nTræner i et stykke tid. Det var dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00594" index="594">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Defeating you will be no easy matter.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00595" index="595">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Is it possible to become more\npowerful by understanding Pokémon?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00596" index="596">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg var sikker på, at du ville vende tilbage.\nJeg fornemmede din tilstedeværelse, ser du.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00597" index="597">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pas på! Bag dig!\nHvad er det?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00598" index="598">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My plan to spook you didn’t go over\nwell at all.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00599" index="599">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You might be tough, but let down\nyour guard at your own risk!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00600" index="600">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wah! That thing curled around your\nneck!\r...Nice scarf, kid!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00601" index="601">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Win or lose...\nWho knows how this’ll go?\rWe’re playing for keeps!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00602" index="602">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I guess wrong far too often.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00603" index="603">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kan ikke komme ind i rillen...\nDet er nok for i dag.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00604" index="604">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg følte mig ikke heldig den anden dag.\nTingene vil være anderledes i dag.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00605" index="605">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Af hensyn til min samling har jeg\ntage imod folk, jeg ved, jeg ikke kan slå.\rDet er, hvad en samler gør.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00606" index="606">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You should boast more about\nthat last attack.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00607" index="607">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er stolt af at have en Pokémon\nandre har ikke.\rÅh, og jeg er også stolt af at vinde\nandenpræmien på Jubilife TV's\fdaglige tegninger.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00608" index="608">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Af hensyn til min samling har jeg\nblive ved med at kæmpe mod mennesker, jeg ikke kan slå.\rDet er, hvad en samler gør.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00609" index="609">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Whaaat? You do!\nYou do have a Pokédex!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00610" index="610">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m so envious of your Pokédex...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00611" index="611">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Trænere har alle mulige slags Pokémon\nmed dem, ikke?\rSå jo flere trænere du kæmper,\njo mere fylder din Pokédex!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00612" index="612">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t have a Pokédex, but that’s\nall right.\rYou come here and show me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00613" index="613">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">To find my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go\neast, west, or any which way!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00614" index="614">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">But they’re my favorite Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00615" index="615">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis du prøver at finde Pokémon\ndu vil, skal du gå overalt!\rHeller ikke kun øst og vest.\nSyd og nord er også vigtige!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00616" index="616">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">For my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go\neast, west, or any which way!\r...Saying that, I’ve been wandering\naround here all this time.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00617" index="617">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh? You want to teach me something\nabout Pokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00618" index="618">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow, er det rigtigt?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00619" index="619">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There are so many kinds of Pokémon.\nI can’t decide which one to pamper.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00620" index="620">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yoohoo, little kid! Can you teach me\nsome more about Pokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00621" index="621">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00622" index="622">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00623" index="623">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00624" index="624">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00625" index="625">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00626" index="626">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00627" index="627">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00628" index="628">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00629" index="629">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00630" index="630">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00631" index="631">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00632" index="632">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00633" index="633">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00634" index="634">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00635" index="635">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00636" index="636">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00637" index="637">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg slumrede, hævder du?\nJeg foregav bare at sove! Hej!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00638" index="638">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gurgle...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00639" index="639">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I feigned a loss!\nHiyah!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00640" index="640">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Am I lost, you ask?\nI merely feigned it! Hiyah!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00641" index="641">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tjek skarpheden af ​​mine kampe\nPokémons bevægelser.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00642" index="642">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve dulled its sharpness...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00643" index="643">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Back to training for us!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00644" index="644">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I sharpened my Pokémon’s moves more\nfor when I saw you again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00645" index="645">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Every drop of sweat I shed makes\nme that much stronger!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00646" index="646">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil ikke tro på dette\nsket, men et tab er et tab.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00647" index="647">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Time to shed some more sweat!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00648" index="648">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’re going to win this time!\rDon’t believe me?\nThen you test it out!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00649" index="649">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hufff-huff, huff-huff.\nWant-huff a battle-huff?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00650" index="650">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Huff-huff, we-huff lose-huff.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00651" index="651">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Bye-huff now-huff.\nHuff-huff, huff-huff.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00652" index="652">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Running-huff is-huff good-huff.\nOver-huff doing-huff it isn’t-huff!\fHuff-huff, huff-huff.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00653" index="653">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Huff-huff, huff-huff.\nWe-huff meet-huff again-huff?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00654" index="654">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll battle anyone.\nThat’s how I’ll get better!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00655" index="655">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du vandt og jeg tabte, men begge dele\ndet har vi fået noget ud af.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00656" index="656">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I en Pokémon-kamp gør den det ikke\nuanset hvor gammel eller ung du er.\rDit køn er heller ikke ligegyldigt.\nSådan noget betyder ikke noget!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00657" index="657">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll battle against people who’ve\nbeaten me again and again.\rBy doing that, we both grow a little\nas Trainers.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00658" index="658">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tager Veilstone Gym\nudfordring. Men først...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00659" index="659">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You made me lose my confidence...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00660" index="660">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tænker på Pokémon hele dagen lang.\nJeg var selvsikker, du ved.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00661" index="661">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, det er dig igen!\rJeg har fået min selvtillid tilbage.\nLad os tage endnu en kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00662" index="662">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er en skattejæger.\rI dag er byttet en sejr fra\ndu!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00663" index="663">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can’t win.\nYou’re too much to take!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00664" index="664">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis man er ude efter skatte, måske\nUnderground er det bedre valg.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00665" index="665">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m a treasure hunter.\rThis time, I will have my trophy:\na victory from you!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00666" index="666">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If I battle now, won’t it mess up my\nusual pace?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00667" index="667">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My pace is completely off...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00668" index="668">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">At holde sig til sit eget mål er mere\nvigtigt end det ser ud til.\rHvis du matcher dit mål med nogen\nellers mister du din identitet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00669" index="669">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, yes, sometimes I do walk.\nI even stop on occasion.\rI am human, after all.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00670" index="670">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Up till now, I’d maintained my pace.\nBut seeing you threw me off!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00671" index="671">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00672" index="672">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00673" index="673">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00674" index="674">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m an ace.\nI can see that you’re an ace, too!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00675" index="675">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Just as I thought...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00676" index="676">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You can pretend to be ordinary, but\nyour eyes tell me another story.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00677" index="677">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A real ace doesn’t get hung up on\ngetting wins.\rA real ace sets sights consistently\nhigher to improve themselves.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00678" index="678">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I always battle for keeps.\nThis is no drill!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00679" index="679">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Good job!\nThat was an excellent battle.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00680" index="680">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If you don’t play for keeps, you’ll\nlose battles you should be dominating.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00681" index="681">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Da jeg tabte til dig sidste gang, var jeg det\nkæmper om beholderne.\rMen denne gang mener jeg det virkelig.\nDette er seriøst for holder!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00682" index="682">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m fully kitted up and equipped!\nAnytime will be fine!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00683" index="683">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hunh?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00684" index="684">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Perhaps I should maybe change into\na more comfy outfit...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00685" index="685">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m fully equipped again today!\nAnytime you’re ready will be fine!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00686" index="686">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">For at være klar til at besvare ethvert opkald!\nAt være klar til at tage imod enhver udfordring!\rSådan er en træners måde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00687" index="687">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How disappointing...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00688" index="688">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kan lave alle forberedelserne\nverden, men hvis det ikke virker, så er det\fvirker ikke.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00689" index="689">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I got everything ready so we could\nhave a rematch whenever you come.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00690" index="690">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m skiing right now, but OK.\nAs we Skiers say, “Spur thing!”\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00691" index="691">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...I’ve hit an ice patch!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00692" index="692">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I quite enjoyed that battle!\nLet us meet again. Slalom!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00693" index="693">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det kan godt være, vi falder på sne, men hvorfor ikke?\nDet er på "spore" i øjeblikket!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00694" index="694">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er du nybegynder?\nEller er du i stand til det?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00695" index="695">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I never expected you to be an\nexpert...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00696" index="696">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du ved, hvordan du spiller din Pokémon\nmed kant!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00697" index="697">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Knowing you to be an expert,\nI challenge you to a rematch!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00698" index="698">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What’s fun about winter?\nNumber one, skiing!\fNumber two, Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00699" index="699">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Snivel...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00700" index="700">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis det var på ski, ville jeg ikke tabe.\nJeg burde stå på ski med min Pokémon...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00701" index="701">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re a better Trainer than a skier.\nBut I’ll challenge you again anyway!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00702" index="702">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How do you expect to battle in this\nheavy snow?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00703" index="703">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The winds of victory shifted...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00704" index="704">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er så koldt her, men her er du,\nklædt alt let på.\rJeg tror, ​​at I børn er gjort hårdere\nend folk på min alder.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00705" index="705">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Why would you wander around here?\nYou must really like this area.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00706" index="706">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can withstand this cold. That means\nI can take any kind of attack!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00707" index="707">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad? Det er slut, siger du?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00708" index="708">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh gud, det her er slemt! Det tror jeg, jeg er\nat miste følelsen i hele min krop!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00709" index="709">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh? I’ve seen your face before.\nWhat say we battle?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00710" index="710">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Denne forkølelse er men intet sammenlignet\ntil ilden, der brænder i mit hjerte!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00711" index="711">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your heart burns as hot as mine!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00712" index="712">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The weather clears up sometimes.\nThe view is breathtaking then.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00713" index="713">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’ll come at you with our hearts\nablaze!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00714" index="714">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wh-what is it?\nP-Pokémon battle?!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00715" index="715">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Puha...\nDu er i live, er du ikke?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00716" index="716">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Omkring disse dele, måske pga\naf al sneen er der mange\ffolkeeventyr om hjemsøgelser...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00717" index="717">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This isn’t like last time. See how\nmuch I’ve trained since then!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00718" index="718">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil vise dig de teknikker, jeg havde\ntromlede ind i mig på skiskolen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00719" index="719">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t believe it...\nMy techniques were rebuffed...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00720" index="720">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I should have enrolled in a Pokémon\nTrainers’ school...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00721" index="721">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Since I lost to you last time,\nI redid my training at ski school!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00722" index="722">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We Skiers feel Mother Nature through\nthe soles of our feet!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00723" index="723">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I got a good taste of your power!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00724" index="724">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Trainers get an appreciation of life\nthrough Pokémon. At least I think so.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00725" index="725">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vidste, du var på vej hertil.\nJeg mærkede det med mine fodsåler!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00726" index="726">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har stået på ski med Pokémon siden\nJeg var kun fem år gammel.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00727" index="727">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, um, wait... What?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00728" index="728">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The scenery doesn’t change very much\naround here. Don’t go getting lost!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00729" index="729">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh... Did you maybe get lost again?\nYou should pay more attention!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00730" index="730">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Regnfulde dage får mig til at føle mig blå...\rMen det øjeblik det begynder at sne,\nJeg er så glad som muligt!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00731" index="731">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The conditions weren’t very good.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00732" index="732">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan nogen af ​​dine Pokémon bruge det\nskjult træk for at bestige klipper?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00733" index="733">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You really must like snow.\rAfter all, if you didn’t, I doubt that\nyou’d come here so often!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00734" index="734">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Poof!\rYou’ve got a good eye spotting me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00735" index="735">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You also saw through my weak\nspots...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00736" index="736">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll play with my Pokémon--even in a\nblizzard!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00737" index="737">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Poof!\rYou saw through my camouflage again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00738" index="738">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er flere slags ninjaer.\nEr du en Iga eller en Kouga ninja?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00739" index="739">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m not much of a ninja either way...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00740" index="740">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I wonder why everyone stops being\na ninja when they grow up?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00741" index="741">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg smedede min viljestyrke i sneen!\nSe min sneklædte magt!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00742" index="742">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">To make sure I’m more agile,\nI always dress light!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00743" index="743">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Akhoo!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00744" index="744">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I might have to go home and dress\nwarmer than this...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00745" index="745">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m sticking it out and staying lightly\ndressed!\r</language>
	</row>
