	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00758" index="758">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yeah, yeah...\nNothing’s biting!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00759" index="759">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00760" index="760">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Når intet bider, det smarte\nat gøre er bare at kalde det en dag.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00761" index="761">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yeah, yeah...\nNothing’s biting today either.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00762" index="762">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00763" index="763">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00764" index="764">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00765" index="765">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00766" index="766">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00767" index="767">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00768" index="768">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00769" index="769">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00770" index="770">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Udendørs fiskeri for sejren!\rAt råbe hjælper ikke mit fiskeri,\nmen råb jeg skal!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00771" index="771">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gwaaah!\nThis is hurting!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00772" index="772">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, rigtigt... Min råb er skræmmende\nvæk Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00773" index="773">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Super outdoor fishing!\nShouting still doesn’t help!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00774" index="774">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lad det rokke!\nDet er kampens rytme!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00775" index="775">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Can you hear it?\nThat’s my guitar weeping...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00776" index="776">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m too torn up to sing anymore...\nI am so cool that way...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00777" index="777">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Rock ’n’ roll!\nWe’ll beat it out again!\fOur rhythm of battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00778" index="778">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En mand af havet er også en mand af\nPokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00779" index="779">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ankre væk!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00780" index="780">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve got what it takes to be\na Trainer among Trainers!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00781" index="781">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Rudder hard to starboard!\nHold on! Nobody go overboard!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00782" index="782">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00783" index="783">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00784" index="784">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00785" index="785">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00786" index="786">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00787" index="787">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00788" index="788">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00789" index="789">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00790" index="790">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00791" index="791">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I love my inner tube.\nSo I admire jellyfish Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00792" index="792">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m drifting away...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00793" index="793">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I wish Professor Rowan would\ngive me a Pokédex.\rBut that old guy looks kind of\nscary.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00794" index="794">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg elsker mit indre rør.\nSå jeg beundrer vandmænds Pokémon.\rVil du ikke hænge ud med os og bare\nbov rundt på bølgerne?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00795" index="795">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can’t swim without my floaty.\nBut my Pokémon sure can!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00796" index="796">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">They weren’t tough, my Pokémon...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00797" index="797">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My mommy said that Professor Rowan\nis really kindhearted.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00798" index="798">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh! Du er træneren, der spillede\nhos os før!\rKan du se, om mine Pokémon er vokset\nstærkere?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00799" index="799">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I only live to swim. Teach me what’s\nso fun about Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00800" index="800">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow, det var sjovt!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00801" index="801">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll try swimming with Pokémon next.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00802" index="802">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yo! You’re that Trainer who taught\nme how fun Pokémon can be.\rLet’s have another battle, you and\nme!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00803" index="803">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">On your marks, get set...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00804" index="804">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Owowowow!\nMy leg cramped up!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00805" index="805">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I forgot to do my stretching\nexercises...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00806" index="806">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej, jeg ventede på dig!\nParat? På dine mærker, gør dig klar...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00807" index="807">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">OK! Get your breathing in order!\nOK! You’re ready to go!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00808" index="808">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I let my momentum falter...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00809" index="809">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Listen, I have something important to\nsay to you.\rDon’t drown in your own talent.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00810" index="810">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">OK! Du er klar til at gå!\nDenne gang går jeg efter sejren!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00811" index="811">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Swimming is a full-body exercise.\nYou should swim, too!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00812" index="812">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sunk like a stone!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00813" index="813">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, Pokémon’s one thing, but you\nshould take up swimming, too!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00814" index="814">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hiya, Pokémon-riding Trainer!\nYou should be swimming like me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00815" index="815">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Den menneskelige krop flyder lettere ind\nhavet, så det er nemt at svømme!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00816" index="816">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The water’s too salty!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00817" index="817">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve got that sinking feeling...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00818" index="818">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pokémon can stay afloat even while\ncarrying someone. That’s so cool!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00819" index="819">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg ser det måske ikke nu, men jeg er en\nstjerne. Jeg er altid sammen med min Pokémon.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00820" index="820">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I lost, but at least I had fun.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00821" index="821">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis det var en undervands Pokémon\nvis, jeg ville have skinnet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00822" index="822">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, hej! Er du tilbage for at se vores\nPokémon show igen?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00823" index="823">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I bought a new bikini!\nIt’s this year’s newest model!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00824" index="824">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Psssssh!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00825" index="825">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I made a mistake buying this bikini...\nIt’s a little too tight...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00826" index="826">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Did I show you already?\nMy bikini, new for this year!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00827" index="827">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00828" index="828">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00829" index="829">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00830" index="830">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00831" index="831">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00832" index="832">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00833" index="833">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00834" index="834">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00835" index="835">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well? Does it look like I’m swimming\ngracefully?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00836" index="836">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m finally feeling fatigued...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00837" index="837">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kan se ud som om jeg svømmer\nyndefuldt, men under overfladen\fJeg sparker rasende.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00838" index="838">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du blev tiltrukket af min yndefulde\nsvømte igen, var du ikke?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00839" index="839">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vand-type Pokémon kommer i en fantastisk\nforskellige former og størrelser.\rJeg vil vise dig vand-Pokémonen det\nJeg har valgt for mig selv!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00840" index="840">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can’t boast when I lose...\nI’m so disappointed...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00841" index="841">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sure I lost, but watch me! I’ll get\ntougher with water Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00842" index="842">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This time, my water Pokémon will show\nyou why I’m so proud of them!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00843" index="843">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hey. I like fishing.\nBut my true love is battling!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00844" index="844">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Slosk!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00845" index="845">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If you don’t know how to fish, you’re\nmissing half of life’s enjoyment.\rIf you don’t know Pokémon...\nYou’re missing out on all of it!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00846" index="846">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Come on, battle me again!\nYou know I love to fish and battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00847" index="847">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00848" index="848">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00849" index="849">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00850" index="850">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Folk betragter mig som en es-træner.\rLad mig demonstrere de færdigheder, der\ngav mig den titel!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00851" index="851">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m burning with jealousy over your\nraw talent!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00852" index="852">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tror, ​​at fortsætte indsatsen\nbedre dig selv er et talent i sig selv.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00853" index="853">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Last time, you beat me before I had\na chance to show you my skill.\rThis time, I’ll show you why they\nconsider me an ace!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00854" index="854">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh? You intend to beat me?\nI am an ace, you know.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00855" index="855">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see...\nI have to concede defeat.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00856" index="856">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">To not be depressed by a loss...\nThat’s one trait of an ace.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00857" index="857">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ace Trainers always work to improve\ntheir natural-born talents.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00858" index="858">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Skal du til Pal Park?\rDet er ikke i orden, at du skal gå\nfør en samler som mig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00859" index="859">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re one enthusiastic Trainer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00860" index="860">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pal Park, huh? I wonder what kinds\nof Pokémon you can see there?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00861" index="861">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hør, gik du til Pal Park?\nHvordan var det? Hvordan var det?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00862" index="862">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er midt i fiskeriet, men OK.\nJeg vil med glæde synke dig.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00863" index="863">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Whooah!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00864" index="864">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Den, der slap væk, var en stor\nen...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00865" index="865">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Once I hook it, no fish gets away\nfrom me!\rA Trainer walking by also can’t get\nfree of my clutches!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00866" index="866">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hi, traveler!\nHow would you like to battle?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00867" index="867">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You sure showed me up.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00868" index="868">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I like to fish.\nYou’re a traveler.\rFarewell, until we meet again!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00869" index="869">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hi, traveler!\rI’ve forgotten your name, but we’ve\nbattled before, haven’t we?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00870" index="870">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m getting bored of fishing.\nLet’s have a quick battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00871" index="871">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve been done in...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00872" index="872">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Thanks, Trainer.\nThat was a good change of pace.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00873" index="873">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yo! Jeg kan huske, hvordan vores kamp var en\ngod ændring af tempo før.\rLad os tage endnu en hurtig kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00874" index="874">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis jeg stirrer på vandoverfladen\nfor længe begynder jeg at glemme hvad\fDet gjorde jeg i første omgang.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00875" index="875">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t know how, but I lost!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00876" index="876">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, right...\nI was fishing, wasn’t I?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00877" index="877">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Da jeg så op fra at stirre på\nvandoverfladen, så jeg dit ansigt.\rJeg er ikke sikker på, hvad jeg lige var\ngør, men vil du kæmpe?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00878" index="878">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
