		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00996" index="996">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00997" index="997">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00998" index="998">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_00999" index="999">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01000" index="1000">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01001" index="1001">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01002" index="1002">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01003" index="1003">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01004" index="1004">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01005" index="1005">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01006" index="1006">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What’s cool, you might ask? No?\nI’ll tell you anyway: bug Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01007" index="1007">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">It bugs me when people ignore the\nawesome coolness of bug Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01008" index="1008">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">It would seem that coolness alone\ndoesn’t add up to any wins...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01009" index="1009">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Her kommer sværmen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01010" index="1010">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hov...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01011" index="1011">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vidste du det? "Sværm" er navnet\naf en Pokémon-evne.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01012" index="1012">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My senses tingle...\nI’ve spotted a rare Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01013" index="1013">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Awawawawah...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01014" index="1014">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg troede det var en sjælden Pokémon, men\ndet viste sig kun at være en træner!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01015" index="1015">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’re just out on a power walk!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01016" index="1016">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, you!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01017" index="1017">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Eewww, grimt! Der er kun fejl\nPokémon i skoven...\rJeg glemte også at købe nogle modgift.\nDet er bare det værste nogensinde!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01018" index="1018">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When a Trainer and a Pokémon bond\nas one, a wondrous power is born...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01019" index="1019">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hmm...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01020" index="1020">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There still remain many mysteries yet\nto be solved in this strange world...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01021" index="1021">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En mærkelig tilstedeværelse er blevet mærket...\nDet udgår fra ... dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01022" index="1022">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh! Be one with me, my MEDITITE!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01023" index="1023">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Old Chateau... I sense...\na particularly strong presence there.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01024" index="1024">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see it...\nI see it...\rI see you going down in defeat...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01025" index="1025">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er mig, der er gået ned i nederlag.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01026" index="1026">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Old Chateau...lies abandoned,\nwith none living in its walls...\rAnd yet, and yet, there permeates a\npresence...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01027" index="1027">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Denne skov er mærkelig, du ved...\nDet ser ud til at fylde mig med energi...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01028" index="1028">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your victory...\nThere is nothing strange about it.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01029" index="1029">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Forests are mystifying... They seem\nto gather such unexplainable energy.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01030" index="1030">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01031" index="1031">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
