		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01217" index="1217">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01218" index="1218">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01219" index="1219">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01220" index="1220">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01221" index="1221">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01222" index="1222">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01223" index="1223">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01224" index="1224">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01225" index="1225">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er ikke slutningen endnu.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01226" index="1226">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Siger du noget?\nTror du, du har fået mig i et hjørne?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01227" index="1227">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Amazing!\nYou’re very good, aren’t you?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01228" index="1228">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fnise! Du fandt mig!\nSelvfølgelig, lad os kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01229" index="1229">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Aww, boo!\nLook, you’ve beaten me!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01230" index="1230">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Giggle! There’s only our Gym Leader\nleft. Go on, don’t be afraid!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01231" index="1231">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A forest inside a Gym...\nShocking, isn’t it?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01232" index="1232">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg ville slå dig, mens du\nvar stadig i en tilstand af chok...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01233" index="1233">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">OK, den næste træner er ved slutningen,\nforbi to kampesten.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01234" index="1234">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My Grass-type Pokémon can dole out\nspecial attacks...\rI won’t let you win easily!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01235" index="1235">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The more beautiful a flower,\nthe faster it withers...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01236" index="1236">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, det er rigtigt...\nEt tip om den næste træner...\rI midten af ​​tre træer.\nDet er mit tip. Held og lykke.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01237" index="1237">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Even concealed, there is no hiding\nthe aroma of flowers.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01238" index="1238">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Just like your inability to conceal\nyour abundant skill.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01239" index="1239">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your next opponent is under four\nflowers.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01240" index="1240">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hey! That there!\nThat was a good move!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01241" index="1241">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This is where it gets exciting!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01242" index="1242">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hunwah!\nIt’s gone and ended!\rHow will I say this... I want more!\nI wanted to battle a lot more!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01243" index="1243">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har landet flest fisk Pokémon\ni verden. Jeg er den næste!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01244" index="1244">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">At være nummer et i verden gør det ikke\nbetyder noget...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01245" index="1245">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I figure I got too wrapped up in\nfishing and neglected training.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01246" index="1246">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har herredømme over det utrolige\nvands kraft. Du vinder ikke!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01247" index="1247">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Men barnet vinder alligevel!\nJeg er lige faldet over!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01248" index="1248">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vandet stiger og falder er vanskeligt,\nmen lad det ikke genere dig.\rHvis du mister dig selv af syne, er det\nnår du er indstillet på at tabe.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01249" index="1249">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har rejst over hele kloden\nmens du hæver Pokémon.\rDette er træningscentret, jeg har valgt.\nDu finder det helt sikkert en håndfuld!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01250" index="1250">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You!\nYou’re a kind of top-class tough!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01251" index="1251">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis du skulle gå jorden rundt,\nJeg er sikker på, at du vil møde hårdere Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01252" index="1252">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Som det rasende hav styrter jeg ned\nog vask alt væk foran mig!\rDet er bare sådan jeg ruller!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01253" index="1253">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">That wave didn’t even wash\nmy hands...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01254" index="1254">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m now becalmed like a waveless\nsea...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01255" index="1255">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min krop er ikke det eneste jeg\narbejde på at skærpe op her.\rJeg arbejder også på min Pokémon og min\nånd!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01256" index="1256">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow, Trainer! You just might be\ntougher than our Gym Leader!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01257" index="1257">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Maybe I’ll do like Wake,\rI mean, Crasher Wake, and wear\nthe same kind of mask.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01258" index="1258">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I want to become a strong Trainer\nlike Crasher Wake!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01259" index="1259">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Groan...\nYou’re too much.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01260" index="1260">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Maybe I’ll do like Wake,\rI mean, Crasher Wake, and use\nthe same kinds of Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01261" index="1261">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
