		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01263" index="1263">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01264" index="1264">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01265" index="1265">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01266" index="1266">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01267" index="1267">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01268" index="1268">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01269" index="1269">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01270" index="1270">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01271" index="1271">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01272" index="1272">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01273" index="1273">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh!\nMen dette er ikke enden, min ven!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01274" index="1274">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m in a bit of a bind, aren’t I?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01275" index="1275">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I shall admit defeat...\nYou are much too strong.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01276" index="1276">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er Karate Quads!\rJeg vil slå et slag for kærligheden med min\nnæve! Hej, looooooooove!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01277" index="1277">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Argh! Knaset!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01278" index="1278">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dine Pokémon er helt sikkert hårde!\rMen vores Gym-leder Maylene vil\nknække dig som en stak mursten!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01279" index="1279">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er Karate Quads!\rJeg vil slå et slag for modet med\nmin knytnæve! Hej, kuraaaaaaaaaaaage!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01280" index="1280">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I couldn’t force my way to victory...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01281" index="1281">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">At overvælde med magt...\nDet er min ideelle beat-down stil.\rSådan virker det tilsyneladende ikke\ndog med Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01282" index="1282">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er Karate Quads!\rJeg vil slå et slag for håbet med min\nnæve! Hej, hooooooooooooop!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01283" index="1283">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We came up short, but not by much.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01284" index="1284">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll have to redo my training, though.\nMaylene’s gonna trample me again...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01285" index="1285">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er Karate Quads!\rJeg vil slå et slag for tårer med\nmin knytnæve! Hej, teeeeeeaaaaaaaar!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01286" index="1286">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m so hungry, kid...\nI don’t have any strength left...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01287" index="1287">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I lost because I didn’t eat\nenough pizza.\r...No. Anything I say will sound\nlike I’m making excuses.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01288" index="1288">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, himlen. Hvad er det her?\nEr dette min sidste Pokémon?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01289" index="1289">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Never give up, never surrender!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01290" index="1290">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du er så fantastisk stærk.\nJeg ved nu, hvorfor jeg har tabt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01291" index="1291">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve been to all sorts of places.\nThat means I know tons of things!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01292" index="1292">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yeah, whatever.\nYou can battle, too...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01293" index="1293">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m gonna visit new places and find\nnew Pokémon so I’ll be a know-it-all!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01294" index="1294">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Seriøst, knægt, hvorfor svarer du ikke\nquizzen ordentligt?\rDu kunne komme til gymnastiklederen\nuden problemer! Spild af min tid.\fNu må jeg slå dig lidt rundt.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01295" index="1295">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I kinda deserved that, didn’t I?\nI gotta stop mouthing off like that...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01296" index="1296">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll remember you and your shifty\nPokémon, too. I’m watching you...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01297" index="1297">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, åh! Vil du kæmpe mod mig?\nOK, så vil jeg gøre mit bedste!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01298" index="1298">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I squeezed out all my power...\nYou’re one impressive challenger.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01299" index="1299">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Look at it this way: you can learn\nsomething from every battle.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01300" index="1300">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ehehe! Du kastede quizzen, så du ville\nkomme i kamp med mig, ikke?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01301" index="1301">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Don’t you know how to take it easy\nor anything? Geesh!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01302" index="1302">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Since you’re here, you might as well\ntake on every Trainer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01303" index="1303">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m not afraid of picnicking anywhere,\nso I’ve learned all sorts of things.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01304" index="1304">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your toughness...\nIt’s something new to me.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01305" index="1305">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har lært, at Pokémon er sjovt\nfor alle leger med dem!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01306" index="1306">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg studerer fag som Pokémon og\nhistorie...\rDu ved, alle de vigtige ting!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01307" index="1307">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, what in the...?\nI didn’t study enough?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01308" index="1308">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You won because of Pokémon type\nmatchups, cool tactics...\rYou know, all sorts of reasons!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01309" index="1309">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve probably studied more about\nPokémon than you.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01310" index="1310">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, you!\nI feel bad that I’m so angry!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01311" index="1311">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg gennemgår årsagerne til, at jeg\ntabt. På den måde vinder jeg næste gang.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01312" index="1312">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Har du ikke en Pokétch?\nEller kneb du med vilje?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01313" index="1313">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gwaah!\nI was done in!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01314" index="1314">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du bliver dog nødt til at vende tilbage.\nDette er en blindgyde.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01315" index="1315">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil bryde isen og bringe\nud af min sidste udvej Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01316" index="1316">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kan mærke din vilje til at vinde, men jeg\nlover dig, at jeg ikke er ved at tabe!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01317" index="1317">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I must say, I’ve warmed up to you!\nI might even admire you a little.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01318" index="1318">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...Det er t-for koldt.\nJeg kan ikke engang mærke min t-tunge.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01319" index="1319">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette resultat...\n...Det er koldt. Bitter kold.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01320" index="1320">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The higher up you slide from, the\nmore speed you’ll have to smash\fthose big snowballs.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01321" index="1321">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min viljestyrke blev formet og tempereret\nved hylende snestorme.\rJeg bringer det til dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01322" index="1322">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You weren’t even fazed...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01323" index="1323">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve battled countless Trainers\nand many more Pokémon still.\rMy spirit has been hardened from all\nthe battles I have fared.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01324" index="1324">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er Gymmets trickgulv, der gør dig\nlidt varm under kraven?\rHvis du ikke kan bevare roen\nkamp, ​​vil du fryse.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01325" index="1325">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du var overraskende sej...\nJeg har i hvert fald mine varme støvler.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01326" index="1326">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Din Pokémon ser så varm ud i kamp.\nSå varme, de er fede! Hahah!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01327" index="1327">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Føler du kulden af ​​træthed?\rEn god træner går efter sejren nr\nlige meget hvad deres tilstand er!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01328" index="1328">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er rigtigt. En god træner vil vinde,\nuanset hvordan situationen måtte være.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01329" index="1329">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Trænerens følelser...\nPokémonens følelser...\rHvis de er en og samme, dig\nvil aldrig tabe.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01330" index="1330">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01331" index="1331">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01332" index="1332">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01333" index="1333">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01334" index="1334">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01335" index="1335">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01336" index="1336">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Here it comes!\nGet ready for my trump card!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01337" index="1337">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Shocking... I didn’t see this coming!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01338" index="1338">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har fået mig til at slå...\rDit ønske og den ædle måde\ndin Pokémon kæmpede for dig...\rJeg følte mig endda begejstret under vores\nkamp.\rDet var en meget god kamp.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01339" index="1339">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow! I’m surprised you’ve come this\nfar, but you’ll have to turn back.\rThere isn’t any chance that you\ncould ever beat me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01340" index="1340">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad gør din Pokémon\nså speciel?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01341" index="1341">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">As a challenger, you’re one tough\nTrainer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01342" index="1342">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg leder ikke kun efter hårde\nTrænere til kamp.\rJeg har kæmpet her pga\nJeg vil gerne mærke suset!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01343" index="1343">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your power is thrilling...\nI’m thrilled down to my toes!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01344" index="1344">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er så glad for, at der er Pokémon!\rDer er ikke meget andet, der giver mig\nden spænding, som Pokémon gør!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01345" index="1345">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I want to win! I channel that desire\nthrough my guitar!\rI want to win! That desire makes\nmy Pokémon a star!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01346" index="1346">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We couldn’t win...\nNo encores for us...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01347" index="1347">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Trainer’s desire to win!\rIf you don’t lose that, there’s\nno limit on what you can become!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01348" index="1348">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gnist!\rDette er, hvad vores Gym Leader gjorde\ntil gymnastiksalen af ​​kedsomhed!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01349" index="1349">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Spark...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01350" index="1350">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi manglede energi...\rNej, vi manglede mere end det. Vi\nville ikke have sejren nok.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01351" index="1351">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Whether you’re a Trainer or a\nGuitarist, it takes dedication to\fimprove your mad skills!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01352" index="1352">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My skills seem to have let me down.\nI must have been out of tune!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01353" index="1353">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Den måde du kæmper på, kan jeg mærke\nhjertet af rock and roll.\rSig mig, er du måske fan af\nrocker ud?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01354" index="1354">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Se på den måde, jeg er klædt på.\nKan du ikke se, at jeg er hardcore?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01355" index="1355">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I was being serious!\nDon’t laugh at me! I mean it!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01356" index="1356">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I dress this way so I can learn to\nthink like an electric Pokémon.\rWhy don’t you give it a try?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01357" index="1357">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette er det hårdeste træningscenter i Sinnoh.\rDet er derfor, jeg er her - for at lære\nbedste kampteknikker der findes!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01358" index="1358">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...You’re tough.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01359" index="1359">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du viste mig lige, at der er\nstadig meget jeg mangler at lære.\rPokémons verden er dyb!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01360" index="1360">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan du nå gymnastikslederen?\nEr du sikker nu?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01361" index="1361">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The gears spin round and round...\nI spin down and out...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01362" index="1362">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vores Gyms trick-gange er sikre\nat få dit hoved til at snurre!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01363" index="1363">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My dragon Pokémon chose to become\npowerful here. They sure like it!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01364" index="1364">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your battle style...\nSo savage...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01365" index="1365">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er flere år siden, jeg tog afsted\nDragens Hule.\rJeg er nødt til at sige, dine Pokémon er\ni topklassen for hårdhed.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01366" index="1366">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My dragon Pokémon chose to remain\nhere to become powerful.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01367" index="1367">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er noget ved dig...\nDu er ikke hvem som helst.\rJeg udfordrer dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01368" index="1368">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re at a different level of\nexpertise for sure!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01369" index="1369">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve won countless times...\nThat has made you very powerful.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01370" index="1370">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There’s something about you...\nYou still remain extraordinary.\rI challenge you again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01371" index="1371">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I constantly analyze Pokémon and\nvarious battles on my laptop.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01372" index="1372">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...Things don’t always work out\naccording to my calculations...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01373" index="1373">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I had a lot of fun battling with\nyou, though.\rI wonder if I can analyze the\nbattle data properly?\rI could use a rematch to get\nsome additional data.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01374" index="1374">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I analyzed our last battle on my\nlaptop.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01375" index="1375">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Af en eller anden grund blev jeg trukket her,\nog det er her jeg mødte dig...\rJeg vil gerne vide, hvad alt dette betyder!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01376" index="1376">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see...\rSo that’s what it means...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01377" index="1377">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I feel... I feel some sort of a mystic\npresence emanating from here...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01378" index="1378">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Why have you come back to this spot?\nI want to know what all this means!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01379" index="1379">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Der er intet her... Og dog\nder lurer en magt...\rBlev du også tiltrukket af det?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01380" index="1380">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Den kraft, der slumrer i dig...\nDet er faktisk ret fantastisk...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01381" index="1381">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et sted hvor intet andet eksisterer...\rEt sted som det er bedre egnet\nat vække kraften indeni.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01382" index="1382">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Do you see now?\nYou’ve come back again.\rThere must be something that draws\nyou to this place...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01383" index="1383">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er ligeglad med hvem du er - ingen\nforstyrrer min skattejagt!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01384" index="1384">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My treasure!\nMy Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01385" index="1385">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I heard there’s an intriguing stone\nmonument around, so I came running.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01386" index="1386">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er her stadig...og søger stadig\nfor skatte.\rDog en kamp med dig\ner en skat jeg ikke kan gå glip af!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01387" index="1387">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En mand, der står alene, jeg vender ud mod havet\nog træne.\rDisse næver blev hugget på den måde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01388" index="1388">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My training and my fists weren’t\nenough to defeat you!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01389" index="1389">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Argh! I stedet for at træne mig selv,\nJeg skulle have trænet min Pokémon!\rAlt hvad jeg har lavet det sidste år\nstirrer ud over havet!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01390" index="1390">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh, det er længe siden!\rJeg har strammet mine næver\nmod havet, ligesom før!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01391" index="1391">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har set utallige trænere og\nendnu flere Pokémon!\rSå hvad er du for en træner?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01392" index="1392">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see...\nSimply outstanding.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01393" index="1393">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har set utallige trænere og\nendnu flere Pokémon.\rDu er en stærk træner.\nDesuden er dit hjerte stærkt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01394" index="1394">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I am indeed a Veteran, but I don’t\nuse that as an excuse to slack off.\rI take pride in challenging those\nwho have bested me before!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01395" index="1395">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh snap!\nSådan er det så?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01396" index="1396">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I like to study a lot...\nI thought I could win...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01397" index="1397">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If you can beat me, I’ll let you join\nmy fan club so you can adore me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01398" index="1398">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Øv! Er du en af ​​de skøre\nfans? Du er helt sikkert bøvlet!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01399" index="1399">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, that’s me and my Pokémon!\nThank you for being such a fan!\rJust so you know, our latest single\nis “Pokémon for World Peace”!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01400" index="1400">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve spotted a charismatic Trainer!\nWe just might have a scoop here!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01401" index="1401">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My camera’s too heavy.\nI couldn’t battle effectively...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01402" index="1402">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">De livlige udtryk på dig og\ndin Pokémons ansigter...\rDet giver helt sikkert noget fantastisk tv!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01403" index="1403">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your spirit’s vibes, man... I can feel\nthat you’ve got rock in your soul!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01404" index="1404">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You beat me, man, but...\nI feel totally amped to jam harder!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01405" index="1405">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Rock handler om din ånd!\nKamp handler også om ånd!\fDet er derfor, kampe rocker! Rawk!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01406" index="1406">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re live on camera, but try\nto act natural, OK?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01407" index="1407">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The camera is our witness!\nIt’s recorded our defeat...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01408" index="1408">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil gerne tage de optagelser og\nfå det udsendt over hele verden.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01409" index="1409">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Two Pokémon! If you had two Pokémon,\nwe’d have a great scene to shoot!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01410" index="1410">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Så lad os begynde og finde ud af hvad\nen slags træner du er!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01411" index="1411">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har en superstjerne kvalitet!\nDu kan helt sikkert blive en berømthed!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01412" index="1412">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I lost, but I’m totally thrilled!\nWe just made some great TV!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01413" index="1413">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh nej. Det vi leder efter er dig\ni aktion med to Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01414" index="1414">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er vi alle klar til at have det sjovt?\nDet er jeg bestemt! Har du det ikke sjovt?!\fLad os gøre det sjovt! OK?! Mwahahah!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01415" index="1415">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, no, no, no!\nMwahahah?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01416" index="1416">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En klovns makeup er et ansigt, der er\ngræder, mens de griner. Mwahahah!\rDet definerer, hvad vi gør!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01417" index="1417">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Po-Po-Pokémon!\nDo you think I’m a real Pokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01418" index="1418">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pi-pikachu!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01419" index="1419">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I need to find a way to get more into\nthe character of a Pokémon...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01420" index="1420">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Slut dig til mig i denne rapport på stedet,\nlive på scenen for en kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01421" index="1421">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Medierne er offeret!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01422" index="1422">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Interviews handler om at tage\ninitiativ. Folk skal vide det.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01423" index="1423">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvordan er dette vanvid muligt?\nTaber vi to til børn?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01424" index="1424">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This won’t do... Time to retreat.\nThis mission is a failure.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01425" index="1425">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How insolent.\nTake a bite of this, child!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01426" index="1426">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Losing to some child...\nBeing careless cost me too much.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01427" index="1427">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We are gathering Pokémon for\nan astonishing undertaking!\rYour meddling won’t be tolerated!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01428" index="1428">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I feel like I got meddled with...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01429" index="1429">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vores forbløffende forehavende er\nhelt sikkert betagende.\rHvis du nogensinde håber at se det herligt\nafsløring, så bland dig ikke i os!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01430" index="1430">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01431" index="1431">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01432" index="1432">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01433" index="1433">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vores mål er utrolige!\nFor utroligt til at jeg kan forstå!\rJeg vil kæmpe blindt for at forsvare dem,\nog din indtrængen vil ikke blive tilgivet!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01434" index="1434">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What was I fighting for, again?</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01435" index="1435">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad har du imod at tage\nPokémon fra andre?\rSe i enhver mark eller skov!\nDe ting er ikke ligefrem sjældne!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01436" index="1436">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01437" index="1437">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01438" index="1438">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01439" index="1439">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sorry, deary! Team Galactic doesn’t\naccept children as members!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01440" index="1440">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">B-but, deary, you’re just a kid!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01441" index="1441">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You wanted to go up?\nWell, why didn’t you?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01442" index="1442">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lad os se, hvor god denne Pokémon er!\nJeg stjal den fra en svag træner.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01443" index="1443">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad er det her?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01444" index="1444">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wimpy little Pokémon...\rWhen I get promoted, I’ll demand\nbetter stolen Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01445" index="1445">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvorfor, tak!\rVi elsker, når folk kommer til os\nat donere deres Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01446" index="1446">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What do you think you’re doing?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01447" index="1447">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You can catch Pokémon anywhere.\nWhat’s so special about them?\rTrainers that lose theirs should\nquit whining and catch some more!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01448" index="1448">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01449" index="1449">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01450" index="1450">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01451" index="1451">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette sted vrimler med UNOWN...\nDer skal være en mening med dette.\rSandheden er derude...\nJeg starter min søgen med at kæmpe mod dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01452" index="1452">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The search must continue!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01453" index="1453">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">jeg giver op. Jeg har ikke tænkt mig at rack min\nhjerne over betydningen af ​​dette sted.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01454" index="1454">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can’t explain it...\nBeing here compels me to battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01455" index="1455">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hunh?!\nWhat was I just doing?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01456" index="1456">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Selvom de er væk, deres ønske\nat kæmpe lever videre?\rDvæler Pokémon-ånderne stadig?\nEr det hvad det er?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01457" index="1457">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I need to shake off my sorrow...\nPlease, battle with me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01458" index="1458">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My sorrow has deepened...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01459" index="1459">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil aldrig glemme den tid, jeg brugte\nmed min Pokémon...\rIkke engang et øjeblik.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01460" index="1460">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det gør ingen forskel, hvor vi er.\rHvis du har Pokémon med dig,\nJeg synes, du burde kæmpe.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01461" index="1461">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve got a lot of giddyap and go\nin you!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01462" index="1462">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Over et langt liv vil du være sikker\nat få nogle sørgelige farvel.\rMen jeg regner med, at der også er nogle\nnye begyndelser.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01463" index="1463">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hahaha! Jeg er bange for, at I ikke er matchende\nfor os med jus’ en af ​​dem Pokémon!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01464" index="1464">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min Pokémon er en livlig en.\nLad mig vise dig hvor meget!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01465" index="1465">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Godt! Er du ikke den livlige!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01466" index="1466">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">De graver her i Lost Tower...\nLige her, inde i mit hjerte...\rDet er de steder, hvor min\nPokémon forbliver...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01467" index="1467">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You haven’t got yerself two\nPokémon?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01468" index="1468">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mine Pokémon blev taget fra mig...\nTeam Galactic gjorde det...\rLige siden har jeg aldrig tilgivet\nderes ansigter...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01469" index="1469">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gwaaaaaah!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01470" index="1470">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg gør ikke min Pokémon nogen tjeneste\nved at ødelægge dens hukommelse på denne måde...\rJeg kan ikke tumle rundt for evigt.\nJeg skal videre og vende siden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01471" index="1471">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mike: I can’t embarrass myself again.\nNot in front of my girlfriend!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01472" index="1472">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mike: Awww, jeez.\nMan, that’s a downer...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01473" index="1473">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mike: Coming here again brings back\nall kinds of memories of me and Nat.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01474" index="1474">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mike: Du kan ikke kæmpe med os.\nIkke med én Pokémon i hvert fald.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01475" index="1475">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nat: I don’t want to look bad again.\nNot when my boyfriend is watching!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01476" index="1476">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nat: This makes me feel hollow\ninside... Oh, so hollow...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01477" index="1477">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nat: Pokémonen, der bragte mig og\nMike er sammen begravet her...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01478" index="1478">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nat: You do have at least two\nPokémon, don’t you?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01479" index="1479">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Waah! Ghost! Get away! Eek!\nHelp me, team!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01480" index="1480">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hey...\nYou’re no ghost...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01481" index="1481">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg var nødt til at komme her, fordi jeg tabte\nen tur med nogle børn i skolen.\rTaberen skulle til tops og\nbring en HM tilbage...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01482" index="1482">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Beating you would be my 100th\nstraight win! Here’s to a fun battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01483" index="1483">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du ved ikke hvor frustrerende det er\nat tabe nu, efter alt det arbejde!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01484" index="1484">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I wish I could beat Maylene in\nVeilstone City one day...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01485" index="1485">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yeah, I like to camp! So what?\nLet’s battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01486" index="1486">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I should’ve just stuck to\ncamping out here...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01487" index="1487">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When I’m with my Pokémon, I can camp\njust about anywhere I want!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01488" index="1488">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis vi kæmper her, vil din Pokémon det\nblive stærkere, og det bliver mit også.\rDet er en god ting for os begge.\nHvad kan man ikke lide? Lad os kaste ned!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01489" index="1489">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You know, I would have really enjoyed\na win there. Would’ve been real nice.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01490" index="1490">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Denne mine er blevet forladt, men\nnu er det hjemsted for mange Pokémon.\rAlting finder vel en plads\nat ringe hjem en dag...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01491" index="1491">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tough Pokémon...\nTough Trainers...\rYou tell me, where else can I find\na place as good as this to train?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01492" index="1492">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det var godt.\nDu har knyttet godt til din Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01493" index="1493">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tough Pokémon...\nTough Trainers...\rA strong spirit and a tight bond...\nThere is so much to train for.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01494" index="1494">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil banke næverskrækken ind\njer alle i karatestil, punk!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01495" index="1495">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m so sorry...\nI got a bit mouthy there, didn’t I?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01496" index="1496">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">So, I’m gonna try and shatter steel!\rI wonder how many more years it\nwould take for me to do that?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01497" index="1497">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Every good Hiker gets a boost of\nenergy when surrounded by boulders!\rWrooooar! Coming at you!\nLet me blow off some steam!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01498" index="1498">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Whew... Crazy, delicious sugar!\nI think I’ve calmed down now...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01499" index="1499">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis det kaldes et bjerg, kan du\nvær sikker på, at jeg vil bestige den.\rSelvom det er et bjerg af mad, så gør jeg det\nhold stadig mit flag på toppen!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01500" index="1500">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Når du er oppe i bjergene,\nen kamp ville gøre for en ordentlig hilsen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01501" index="1501">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yahoo!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01502" index="1502">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Faktisk, når du er oppe i\nbjerge, en simpel hi'd gøre hvis\fdu går forbi nogen.\rÅh, og dette er ikke bjergene.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01503" index="1503">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">May we have a battle, please?\rIt will be something to lighten up this\nboring picnic with.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01504" index="1504">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi kommer ikke til at vinde, hvis vi spiller\nsådan rundt...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01505" index="1505">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m going home to play with my\nPokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01506" index="1506">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The working-class hero says hi!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01507" index="1507">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The working-class hero waves bye...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01508" index="1508">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har arbejdet her længe\nsiden, før den lukkede ned.\rJeg arbejdede på jernværket i nærheden\nFloaroma Town også.\rDu kan sige, at jeg er trukket af jern\nsom ved magnet!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01509" index="1509">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mens jeg sørger for, at elevatorerne er\nsikker, jeg vil fokusere på en kamp med dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01510" index="1510">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A-OK! Looks safe to me!\nNot a problem in sight!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01511" index="1511">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tjekker rutinemæssigt elevatorerne her.\nDu kan være sikker på deres sikkerhed!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01512" index="1512">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej! Dette er ingen legeplads!\nHvis du vil spille, så kæmp mig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01513" index="1513">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You played me like an amateur!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01514" index="1514">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">De ville lukke dette sted\nop, så ingen kunne komme ind.\rMen, de lod det stå åbent så folk og\nPokémon kan samles her.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01515" index="1515">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Canalave Gym folks use this place\nas their training grounds.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01516" index="1516">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Måske skulle jeg tage til gymnastiksalen og\narbejde derude...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01517" index="1517">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Roark spent his childhood playing\nhere, I think...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01518" index="1518">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Humph! You’re lost, aren’t you?\nI’ll guide you if you can beat me.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01519" index="1519">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I said I’m going to win!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01520" index="1520">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er ikke fortabt, siger jeg dig!\njeg camperer! Det er min historie!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01521" index="1521">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad? Er du også tabt?\nIngen? Det er lige meget.\fLad os tage en hurtig Pokémon-kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01522" index="1522">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ikke fair!\nVi er ikke på samme niveau!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01523" index="1523">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I got separated from my friends...\rI’ve got my Pokémon with me, so I’m\nOK, but...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01524" index="1524">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You look like you might just have\nthe Pokémon I’ve been looking for!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01525" index="1525">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You didn’t have a single Pokémon\nI wanted... You’re no Collector!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01526" index="1526">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m very picky, so I want to collect\nevery Pokémon without anyone’s help.\r...I do have friends, though.\nNo, seriously! I do!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01527" index="1527">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">In deep tunnels and caves, there’re\na couple things you’re sure to see.\rZUBAT and Ruin Maniacs!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01528" index="1528">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your awesome power...\nIt’s mystifying.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01529" index="1529">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har gennemsøgt hver en tomme af dette\nsted... Det meste af det, mens jeg var tabt.\rI hvert fald, hvis der er én ting, jeg kan\nsige, dette sted kan ikke kaldes ruiner!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01530" index="1530">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hush now, lost little Pokémon, don’t\nyou cry.\rI’m here to take care of you!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01531" index="1531">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sniffle... W-who’s crying now?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01532" index="1532">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Apropos at græde, så er jeg sikker på\nhørte gråd dybere nede i hulen.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01533" index="1533">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Look! A Trainer lost in Wayward Cave!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01534" index="1534">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg gik væk fra slagplanen!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01535" index="1535">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Me? No, I’m not lost.\nI live here!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01536" index="1536">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wandering around, I got hungry, so\nI ate some wild mushrooms...\rThey gave me gas, and now I can’t\nstop burping! Bluurrf!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01537" index="1537">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Bleff! Hurk!\nI think...I’m getting better...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01538" index="1538">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I hear there’s a Pokémon that has\nmushrooms growing on its back.\rNot around here, somewhere far away.\nI wonder if they taste any good?</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01539" index="1539">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvor er jeg? Er jeg tabt? Hvem er du?\nEr du en Pokémon-træner?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01540" index="1540">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">OK, so we’re both Trainers.\nThat’s a start, right?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01541" index="1541">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I just wanted to have a picnic under\nthe Cycling Road.\rI didn’t think I would get lost\nin a place like this...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01542" index="1542">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What every good picnic needs is a\ncute setting, good food, and a fun\fbattle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01543" index="1543">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">That wasn’t any fun for me!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01544" index="1544">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Why have a picnic here? I don’t know.\nThere’s no deep meaning to it.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01545" index="1545">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Did you come to play, too?\nWanna play battle with me?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01546" index="1546">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du legede bare med mig!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01547" index="1547">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m playing hide-and-seek here.\nI like some underground tag, too.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01548" index="1548">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The sharp vision of my bird Pokémon\nwill see through your weaknesses!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01549" index="1549">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Har du ikke en akilleshæl?</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01550" index="1550">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I want to become stronger, but only\nwith my favorite Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01551" index="1551">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Lær at håndtere hårde Pokémon\ner genvejen til at blive hård.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01552" index="1552">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">jeg tabte? Men hvordan er det muligt?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01553" index="1553">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Being able to manage any kind of\nPokémon...\rI suppose that makes a good Trainer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01554" index="1554">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Being this tough isn’t good enough.\nYou have to look cool while doing it.\rMastering that makes you an ace!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01555" index="1555">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Made me look bad...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01556" index="1556">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kæmpede så godt jeg kunne.\nJeg var ikke ured med at tabe! ...Højre?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01557" index="1557">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg vil gerne have, at min Pokémon smager\nden sødme, der er sejr.\rJeg har ikke råd til at miste denne!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01558" index="1558">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette nederlag har min bitterhed\ntårer...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01559" index="1559">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har ondt af min sultne Pokémon...\rUndskyld, gutter. Jeg bliver hårdere, så du\nkan nyde smagen af ​​sejr...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01560" index="1560">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I will win. I am sure of it.\nTherefore, you will lose!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01561" index="1561">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">But...\nThis isn’t possible!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01562" index="1562">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du vandt ikke!\nJeg har lige tabt!\rÅh, uanset hvad. Det er det samme...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01563" index="1563">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Let me see what you got there, kid.\nI could give you some advice.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01564" index="1564">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You got way too much!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01565" index="1565">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, I don’t have any advice for\nsomeone as tough as you!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01566" index="1566">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nu skal vi kæmpe, og fra det vil vi\ndukke op en taber...\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01567" index="1567">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01568" index="1568">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I can use psychic powers, but\nbattling isn’t so simple...\rIt takes much more to win!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01569" index="1569">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En kamp er et sammenstød mellem viljestyrke!\rDen, der ønsker at vinde mest\nvil vinde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01570" index="1570">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">But... I thought I could win!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01571" index="1571">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Psykisk kraft...\rDet er svært at tro på noget\nsom du ikke kan se...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01572" index="1572">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Allow me to demonstrate how a true\nPsychic conducts a battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01573" index="1573">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Did I get to show you anything...?\nAnything at all?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01574" index="1574">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How do I use my psychic powers?\rI never use them for dishonest ends.\nI also never do any good deeds...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01575" index="1575">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see it!\nI see a victory for me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01576" index="1576">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The future...is different!\nWhy?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01577" index="1577">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Din indsats har ændret selve\nfremtidens vej!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01578" index="1578">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg trænede alle mine knudrede Pokémons\nved Fighting Dojoen i Kanto!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01579" index="1579">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Totally done for!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01580" index="1580">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’re gonna go ahead and leave...\nYou know, go train elsewhere.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01581" index="1581">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Judo chop!\nPokémon battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01582" index="1582">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wrroar!\nJudo chop defeated!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01583" index="1583">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll forget that we lost!\r...Wait, if I did that, we’d never\nlearn from our mistakes...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01584" index="1584">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What it means to battle...\nIts joys, its sorrows...\fI’ve experienced it all!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01585" index="1585">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My sorrow deepens...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01586" index="1586">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du er måske et barn, men du har undervist\nmig en hel masse. Jeg takker dig ydmygt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01587" index="1587">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll wheel out some wicked Pokémon\nand even wickeder moves!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01588" index="1588">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">All I can manage now is to wheeze\nout a few meek sighs...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01589" index="1589">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t see what my age has to do\nwith playing with Pokémon, frankly.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01590" index="1590">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I let my bird Pokémon carry me to\nwherever. And so, here I am!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01591" index="1591">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Sheesh... Jeg ankommer et nyt sted, og\ndet viser sig at være Battle Zone...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01592" index="1592">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg er født i Hoenn-regionen.\nJeg har først for nylig fløjet hertil.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01593" index="1593">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I let my bird Pokémon do as they\nwish. And so, we train here daily!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01594" index="1594">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min Pokémon voksede op i armene på\nModer Natur. De er hårde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01595" index="1595">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How could you be tougher than\nMother Nature?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01596" index="1596">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det meste af tiden vender mine Pokémon tilbage\ntil deres Poké Balls med det samme.\rMen nogle gange falder de bare i søvn\noven på mit hoved. Det bliver rodet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01597" index="1597">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The desire to win... That should be\nevident in every Trainer!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01598" index="1598">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Drage Pokémons potentiale\ndem øverst på min liste!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01599" index="1599">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Potential doesn’t mean I can win...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01600" index="1600">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A Dragon Tamer Champion...\rI’ll need to train so much more to\neven come close to coming close...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01601" index="1601">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve cranked up my dragon Pokémon’s\npotential!\rI’ve been looking forward to seeing\nyou again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01602" index="1602">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What my Pokémon and I most want...\nVictory!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01603" index="1603">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Arrrgh! My GYARADOS...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01604" index="1604">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I don’t ever want to put my Pokémon\nthrough that again...\rIt got humiliated because I wasn’t\ngood enough...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01605" index="1605">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har slået os én gang før, men vi\nvil ikke begå den samme fejl!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01606" index="1606">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dragon Pokémon er hellige væsener...\nDet har min mester lært mig.\rOg nu vil jeg bevise det for dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01607" index="1607">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Not good enough!\nWe’re still not strong enough!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01608" index="1608">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det er ikke godt nok til en Pokémon\nbare at være hård.\rDet er ikke godt nok for en træner\nbare at arbejde hårdt.\rBegge skal vokse sammen!</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01609" index="1609">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">This time!\rI’ll show you how brilliantly I work\nwith my Pokémon partner!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01610" index="1610">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvordan har du det?\nJeg er en dragetæmmer.\rHvad siger vi, vi sammenligner vores Pokémon\nved hjælp af en kamp?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01611" index="1611">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oops!\nHow very silly of me!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01612" index="1612">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Well, there seems to be an image\nassociated with Dragon Tamers.\rBut personally, I’m really laid back\nand easygoing, you know?\rI figure there’s a whole lot of other\nthings I need to worry about first.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01613" index="1613">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej, hvordan har du det igen?\rHvad siger vi lader vores Pokémon hertug det\nud i en anden kamp?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01614" index="1614">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There is something missing in the\nway I battle...\rI’ve come here to find it.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01615" index="1615">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I see it now...\nI know what I lack.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01616" index="1616">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det har været et privilegium at have kæmpet\nmed dig.\rJeg lærte en uvurderlig lektie af\ndig i dag.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01617" index="1617">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Have you discovered what’s missing in\nyour battles? I have.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01618" index="1618">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg har fået lyst til at kæmpe med dig.\nHåber du er villig til at forpligte dig!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01619" index="1619">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I shouldn’t have paid attention\nto my urge...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01620" index="1620">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Så længe min partner er ved siden af ​​mig,\nJeg er villig til at indtage verden!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01621" index="1621">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The urge to battle you again has\nstruck me. Want to humor me?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01622" index="1622">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Har du kendskab til niveauer\neller statistikken for Pokémon? Nå, det gør jeg!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01623" index="1623">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hmm. I like how you attack.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01624" index="1624">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pokémon og tal...\nHvem bekymrer sig om den ting?\rAt vinde er det vigtige.\nTal er ikke alt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01625" index="1625">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pokémon-kampe afgøres ikke af\ntal.\rDet er det bånd, du deler med dit\nPokémon, der bestemmer resultaterne!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01626" index="1626">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Welcome to my Pokémon show!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01627" index="1627">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Nyd du showet?\nSuper fabelagtig, var det ikke?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01628" index="1628">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll be happy to battle you again!\nLet’s battle again sometime, yeah?</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01629" index="1629">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Welcome to my new Pokémon show!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01630" index="1630">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mit hold er blevet trænet igennem\nog igennem!\rDu ryster, når du ser hvordan\nhårde er de!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01631" index="1631">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m sh-sh-shaking all over...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01632" index="1632">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I fed my gang Protein, Carbos...\nYou name it, I pumped ’em full of it.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01633" index="1633">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hej! Du er den træner, der gik\njeg rystede helt op! Øh-hø!\rDenne gang er det min tur til at forlade dig\nryster over det hele!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01634" index="1634">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve leveled my precious partner this\nfar. I’ll let you see it!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01635" index="1635">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">It needs to be leveled more?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01636" index="1636">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min Pokémon...\rDet er faktisk den allerførste ven\nsom jeg nogensinde har haft.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01637" index="1637">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">...When I close my eyes, I’m taken\nback to that time we lost to you.\rMy partner’s leveled since then.\nI’ll prove it to you!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01638" index="1638">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Værdige modstandere... Søgningen efter\nde driver mig til at rejse langt.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01639" index="1639">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve certainly found a tough\nadversary in you...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01640" index="1640">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">How much you believe in your\nPokémon...\rThat’s a critical factor in how a\nbattle will turn out.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01641" index="1641">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi har stået over for mange udfordrere siden\nvi mødtes, men de var alle svage...\rJeg nyder den hårde modstand\nkun du kan yde!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01642" index="1642">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Please don’t hold anything back.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01643" index="1643">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hmm...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01644" index="1644">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I feel invigorated from that battle,\neven though we lost.\rAfter all, we gave it everything we\nhad.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01645" index="1645">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hello again! Please don’t hold\nanything back--just like before.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01646" index="1646">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er du villig til at kæmpe?\nLad mig se, hvad du har?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01647" index="1647">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your love of Pokémon really shows!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01648" index="1648">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I grew up together with my team,\nright from my childhood.\rAll our memories, we’ve always shared\nthem.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01649" index="1649">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, hi, we meet again.\rMay I see what you’ve done with your\nPokémon?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01650" index="1650">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Verden er enorm, og det er der\nså mange forskellige Pokémons!\rHvilken slags Pokémon er der med dig?\nVenligst, jeg vil gerne se!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01651" index="1651">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Wow, der er Pokémon der\nvidunderlig!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01652" index="1652">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There is always something to like\nabout any Pokémon.\rIt’s so hard to decide which ones\nI should raise.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01653" index="1653">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">If I’m having trouble deciding,\nI go with my favorites!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01654" index="1654">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvilken slags bevægelser har du lært?\nDet fortæller mig, hvor god du er!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01655" index="1655">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yowch!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01656" index="1656">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I heard that somewhere there’s\nsomeone who teaches Pokémon moves.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01657" index="1657">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Have you taught your team any new\nmoves since last time?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01658" index="1658">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When eyes meet...\nThat’s when a battle starts!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01659" index="1659">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You won’t let me win?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01660" index="1660">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg huskede pludselig, hvad det var \nsom da jeg havde min første kamp.\rJeg spekulerer på, hvorfor det skulle være det?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01661" index="1661">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When eyes meet...\nThat’s when a battle starts!\fThat’s what makes us Trainers!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01662" index="1662">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kommer til at vinde!\nDet er den fremtid, jeg så!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01663" index="1663">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det, jeg så i fremtiden, viste sig\nat være sandt...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01664" index="1664">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg tabte, men min vision om fremtiden\ngik i opfyldelse...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01665" index="1665">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kommer til at vinde igen!\nDet er den fremtid, jeg så!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01666" index="1666">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Right after this, you will send out\nPokémon to battle me!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01667" index="1667">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Right after this, I have to pay\nout your prize money...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01668" index="1668">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">What will happen to you after this?\nWhy don’t you do just as you like?\fIt would be more fun that way.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01669" index="1669">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Right after this, you will hurl a Poké\nBall in an astonishingly cool way!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01670" index="1670">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min søgen efter magt bragte mig hertil.\rDet var under ørkensandet det\nJeg forstærkede min krop og sjæl.\rAccepter min udfordring! Uraah!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01671" index="1671">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My spirit is broken...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01672" index="1672">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I thought I couldn’t win before it\nbecame a fact...\rI’ve let down my Pokémon...\rThey go to battle with faith in\ntheir Trainer...</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01673" index="1673">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Denne gang! Denne gang vinder jeg!\nMin ånd er fornyet og stærk!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01674" index="1674">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I have meditated under a waterfall\nto temper my spirit.\rAllow me to demonstrate its strength!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01675" index="1675">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ha-choo! Sniffle...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01676" index="1676">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Al den tid under vandfaldet...\nSynes jeg er blevet forkølet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01677" index="1677">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Siden den dag, jeg tabte til dig, har jeg gjort det\nmediterede under et vandfald!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01678" index="1678">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">People! Nature! Pokémon!\nHarmony is essential!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01679" index="1679">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re A-OK!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01680" index="1680">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Protecting Pokémon and nature.\nThink of what that means.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01681" index="1681">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kan du huske mit slogan?\nMennesker! Natur! Pokémon!\rDet er rigtigt, harmoni er afgørende!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01682" index="1682">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I work to protect beautiful, natural\nenvironments.\rMy Pokémon are my constant\ncompanions while I work.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01683" index="1683">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, my gosh!\nMy poor Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01684" index="1684">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Everyone can do their part to keep\nnature clean. It doesn’t take much.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01685" index="1685">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m on patrol in pristine nature\nwith my Pokémon like usual.\rCome to think of it, you’re always\nwith Pokémon, too.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01686" index="1686">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We go on patrol to make sure there’s\nnothing strange going on.\rAnd occasionally, we battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01687" index="1687">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Mange tak!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01688" index="1688">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You know that Pokémon ability Pickup?\rI think that’s a good way of keeping\nthe environment clean of litter.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01689" index="1689">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Patruljer dag ud og dag ind!\nOg en gang imellem kamp!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01690" index="1690">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I moder naturs omfavnelse,\nmennesker og Pokémon bliver stærke!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01691" index="1691">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Min, du er hård.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01692" index="1692">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du kan vokse dig stærk hvor som helst.\nDet er lige meget, hvor du er.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01693" index="1693">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">By battling tough opponents, both\nTrainers and Pokémon grow tough!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01694" index="1694">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi har vokset os stærke sammen i\nnaturen og i betonjunglen.\rVi gør vores overalt, hvor vi går\nlegeplads!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01695" index="1695">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re fantastically tough,\naren’t you?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01696" index="1696">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Look around you at this wildly\ncontorted terrain.\rIt’s no wonder that Pokémon would\ngrow tough in a place like this.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01697" index="1697">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg synes, jeg er ret hård, men altså\ner du og din Pokémon.\rLad os kæmpe for at se hvem\ner den hårdeste!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01698" index="1698">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er du ved at blive slidt af alt\ndet løb du har løbet?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01699" index="1699">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’re not tired at all?!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01700" index="1700">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The world is full of Pokémon and all\nsorts of Trainers.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01701" index="1701">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad synes du om slaget\nZone?\rDu har mødt så mange Pokémon...\nJeg skal kæmpe mod dig igen!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01702" index="1702">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A Trainer riding a Pokémon!\nI like that! We’ve gotta battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01703" index="1703">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Awesome!\nYou’re a real wild child!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01704" index="1704">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Rider på bølgerne på en Pokémon\ntilbage...\rJa, det er noget at tale om\nom, okay.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01705" index="1705">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Yo, Pokémon-riding Trainer!\nHow about a rematch?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01706" index="1706">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Tjek min fysik! Den ru\nhavet skulpturerede denne fantastiske krop!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01707" index="1707">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Muskler jeg har masser af...\nMen lad os ikke tale om magt.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01708" index="1708">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har brugt din Pokémon\net skjult træk til dig...\rJeg synes, det er virkelig bevægende.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01709" index="1709">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det barske hav her næsten\ndruknede...\rVent, nej, formede min fysik!\nSe hvor buff det er!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01710" index="1710">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Check out my dynamic form!\nVictory is assured!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01711" index="1711">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Åh.\nSådan er det.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01712" index="1712">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Being a good swimmer doesn’t make\nme any better as a Trainer...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01713" index="1713">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hi! You’re that kid who’s great with\nPokémon!\rI’ll battle with an even more dynamic\nform than before! Watch me now!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01714" index="1714">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Me and my Pokémon are pumped up\nand ready to go all out!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01715" index="1715">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Our muscles are deflating...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01716" index="1716">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Overvæld med vores blændende fysik!\nDet var vores spilleplan...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01717" index="1717">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Me and my Pokémon are pumped up!\nSee, our muscles are twitching!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01718" index="1718">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">People keep coming to us for battles.\nI really don’t know why! Teehee!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01719" index="1719">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">OK, vi tabte.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01720" index="1720">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg ville gerne være alene, men tøvede\nvæk umodne drenge på jagt...\rNå, min Pokémon blev hård uden\njeg prøver virkelig selv.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01721" index="1721">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">People still keep coming to us for\nbattles! Why?! Leave me alone!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01722" index="1722">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Er din Pokémon ved at blive voksen?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01723" index="1723">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Maybe too grown up!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01724" index="1724">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ve grown with my Pokémon, too.\nMy swimsuit’s getting a little tight...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01725" index="1725">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Voksede din Pokémon mere?\rMin Pokémon?\nMine har det fantastisk!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01726" index="1726">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m a mermaid who drifts among\nthe waves...\rBut I’m also a playful girl who likes\nto have fun with Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01727" index="1727">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Losing brings tears to my eyes...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01728" index="1728">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A mermaid’s tears are so salty...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01729" index="1729">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I remain a mermaid who drifts among\nthe waves...\rBut I’m also a playful girl who likes\nto have fun with Pokémon!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01730" index="1730">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I want to be with my water Pokémon.\nThat’s why I swim.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01731" index="1731">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Glub glub...\nI’m sinking...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01732" index="1732">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Everyone I know says they have to\ntrain harder and more often.\rI thought so too, but I find it hard\nto get that serious about it.\rBeing with my Pokémon puts me in\na mellow mood, I guess.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01733" index="1733">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I want to be with my water Pokémon.\nThat’s why I want to be stronger!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01734" index="1734">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01735" index="1735">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01736" index="1736">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">garbage</attribute>
		<language name="English" />
		<language name="日本語">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01737" index="1737">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Med én mægtig klap blæser mine fugle\nvæk aggressionens gløder!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01738" index="1738">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det lykkedes ikke at komme fra jorden...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01739" index="1739">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The HM Fly isn’t useful inside caves.\nIt’s such a shame.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01740" index="1740">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dragons and a fiery mountain...\nIt’s a totally classic setup!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01741" index="1741">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Losing isn’t a happy occasion...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01742" index="1742">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My Pokémon seem to like it here\na lot.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01743" index="1743">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Søger du det mytiske\nPokémon også? Så lad os kæmpe!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01744" index="1744">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There’s nothing left...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01745" index="1745">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The mythical Pokémon that sleeps\ndeep in a volcano...\rCould it be a dragon Pokémon?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01746" index="1746">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad det vil sige at vinde kampe...\nDet er det, jeg søger.\fLær mig om du vil!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01747" index="1747">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I grow less certain still...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01748" index="1748">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Måske er der ingen mening med det\nsejr, men alligevel vil jeg kæmpe!\rDet er det, der gør mig til træner!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01749" index="1749">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Being with Pokémon makes me happy.\rAnd when we win, I feel happier\nstill!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01750" index="1750">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’re still happy even when we lose!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01751" index="1751">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hæver Pokémon til det yderste...\nAt have det sjovt med Pokémon...\rFolk skal gøre, hvad der gør dem\nlykkelig. Det er hvad jeg synes!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01752" index="1752">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I was born in Floaroma Town.\nI’m sure thrilled to be here.\rIt took a long time to get here.\nWe’re not going to lose again!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01753" index="1753">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We went down...\nWe couldn’t stick it out...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01754" index="1754">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You can level all you want, but that\nwon’t guarantee you any wins.\rBut we keep trying to get better.\nThat’s what makes us Trainers.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01755" index="1755">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Trainers and Pokémon that gather\nhere aren’t pushovers.\fThey all have tricks up their sleeves!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01756" index="1756">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du er ikke en træner, der kan være det\ntaget let!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01757" index="1757">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The Pokémon you’ll meet here won’t\nmake it easy for you to move onward.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01758" index="1758">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">You’ve come all this way for Pokémon?\nYou must be dedicated.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01759" index="1759">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Your dedication won out.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01760" index="1760">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Pokémonerne her skal kæmpe mod hver\nandet hele tiden.\rDet må være derfor, de er så stærke\ni dette område.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01761" index="1761">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My Pokémon and I are pretty nice,\nbut not when it comes to a battle!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01762" index="1762">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kunne ikke slippe det rigtige mig løs...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01763" index="1763">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">When you’re raising Pokémon, you need\nto be both firm and gentle.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01764" index="1764">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jeg kom her efter at have vundet min vej\ngennem Battle Tower!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01765" index="1765">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">But...\nI had a win streak going...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01766" index="1766">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Træn mere i Battle Tower...\nDet er hvad jeg vil gøre.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01767" index="1767">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We’re all good to go!\nWe just have to battle now!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01768" index="1768">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Aww...\nI’m out of useful items!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01769" index="1769">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">We came completely unprepared for\nthis little adventure...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01770" index="1770">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I had a revelation this morning.\rI knew that I would have a wonderful\nencounter here today.\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01771" index="1771">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">There’s nothing wonderful about this!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01772" index="1772">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Is my sense of premonition nothing\nto write home about?\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01773" index="1773">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’ll use my mystifying psychic power\nto pulverize you!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01774" index="1774">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">That’s what I get for making idle\nclaims...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01775" index="1775">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Psykisk kraft er et mysterium\ntrodser forklaringen.\rMen hvis alt kunne forklares,\ndet ville være en kedelig verden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01776" index="1776">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">My Pokémon can destroy anything.\nAnd you think you can win?!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01777" index="1777">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi var ikke klar til opgaven!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01778" index="1778">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Even though my team could break\nbricks and shatter boulders, they\ffailed to dent your spirits!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01779" index="1779">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hør hylen fra mine jernnæver!\nHejsa! Jeg er vild med karate!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01780" index="1780">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Losing made it clear to me.\nYou’re crazy about Pokémon!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01781" index="1781">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I love seeing people who love Pokémon\nmore than anything!\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01782" index="1782">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvad forventer du at opnå her?\nJeg vil være den, der foretager det opkald!\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01783" index="1783">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du har optjent retten til at være her.\nBåde dig og din Pokémon.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01784" index="1784">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Du finder det måske mærkeligt, men det stinker\naf svovl fra vulkangassen\fer det, der trækker mig her.\n</language>
	</row>
