		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I fully believe in this last one.\nI have no reason to freak out.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_01961" index="1961">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Vi er ikke færdige endnu! Vi kommer ud\naf denne plads, fordi vi er så stramme!\n</language>
