		<language name="English">I’m always with my Pokémon.\rActually, you’re always with your\nPokémon too, aren’t you?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_02016" index="2016">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I’m so beyond bummed out now...\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_02017" index="2017">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">I got a nifty-keen Gym Badge from\nthe Gym Leader in Oreburgh City!\r...Did I show you already?\r</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0558_02018" index="2018">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Oh, I lost! Lalala!\n</language>
	</row>
